OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1777543610
OL,3,CTeenage athlete from Cumbria to
OL,4,Crepresent Great Britain
OL,6,FA teenage athlete from Cumbria is
OL,7,Fpreparing to represent Great Britain
OL,8,Fin two world championships this year.
OL,10,FSam Turney, 16, is a member of
OL,11,FCarlisle's junior triathlon club.
OL,13,FHe is managing a gruelling schedule,
OL,14,Fas he juggles his sporting career and
OL,15,Fstudying for his A-level exams.
OL,17,F"I train roughly 16 hours a week, so
OL,18,Fwith doing school work it's really
OL,19,Fhard to balance everything," Sam said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
