PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1777543610
OL,3,CTeenage athlete from Cumbria to
OL,4,Crepresent Great Britain
OL,6,F"I just like that it's three sports in
OL,7,Fone; nothing else is like it."
OL,9,FSam is aiming to emulate the success
OL,10,Fof his role models - the Brownlee
OL,11,Fbrothers.
OL,13,F"They introduced me to the sport,
OL,14,Fwatching the Olympics. My ultimate
OL,15,Fgoal is to get to the Olympics. Who
OL,16,Fknows if it will happen, but hopefully
OL,17,Fit will."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
