PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1777543610
OL,3,CTeenage athlete from Cumbria to
OL,4,Crepresent Great Britain
OL,6,FFor now, Sam will be competing abroad
OL,7,Fthis year at two international
OL,8,Fathletic events in Abu Dhabi and
OL,9,FPontevedra.
OL,11,FThis September, he'll be in Spain
OL,12,Ftaking part in the World Sprint
OL,13,FTriathlon Championships - a 750m swim,
OL,14,F20km bike, and 5km run.
OL,16,FThen he's off to the United Arab
OL,17,FEmirates in November for the World
OL,18,FSprint Duathlon Championships.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
