CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1777543610
OL,3,CTeenage athlete from Cumbria to
OL,4,Crepresent Great Britain
OL,6,FHis says his family are supporting him
OL,7,Fall the way, both financially and
OL,8,Femotionally.
OL,10,F"Even though he's been chosen to
OL,11,Frepresent Great Britain, it's all self-
OL,12,Ffunded," Sam's dad, Paul Turney, told
OL,13,FITV News Border.
OL,15,F"Your travel, your accommodation, you
OL,16,Fhave to buy the right kit. It's a big
OL,17,Ffinancial commitment, but when he's
OL,18,Fbeen given this opportunity to compete
OL,19,Fat the highest level, we want to
OL,20,Fsupport him."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
