OL,3,CTeenage athlete from Cumbria to
OL,4,Crepresent Great Britain
OL,6,FWhen the 16-year-old is not training
OL,7,Fhimself, he can be found at Carlisle's
OL,8,FSheepmount stadium helping the next
OL,9,Fgeneration of triathletes.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
